  <h1 class="gd-h1">Your First Heliski Day</h1>
  <p class="gd-lede">You are booked, the flights are sorted, and now the only thing left is the not-knowing: how does a heliski day actually unfold? This is a warm, honest walkthrough of your first day on the Troll Peninsula, from the quiet evening before to the last run home &mdash; so you arrive feeling prepared rather than anxious. There is no rigid timetable to memorise and no secret handshake, just a natural flow that the guides have run hundreds of times. Browse our <a href="/packages">packages</a> or picture the whole trip in our guide to heliskiing in <a href="/iceland">Iceland</a>.</p>
</div></section>
